
All KiCad manuals and tutorials have been written using LibreOffice 3.3.2 and
saved in .odt format.

All KiCad manuals are based on the same template which includes a large set of 
styles name OOoxxxxx accessible via:
 Format - Styles and Formatting - Customs Styles

When these documents are edited updated it is important to use only OOoxxxxx styles.

Images throughout the document are linked to externals images saved in the 
folder "pics". Do not embed any picture in the document but instead just link
them. 

